<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am a 55th lvl myrmidon on Luclin.....I just recently got a "Rod of Lamentation".  Since my 2hb was so low we just added it into the daily group pot (crypt farming at its best) and I had the highest roll....giving me first choice.  I picked this out of spite, not intending on using it at all....and while not as good as the original Mourning rod, its still kicks ass.  Was in HS tonite with another friend warrior....and I got to work my 2hb skill.  Now I have 170 2hb skill and get constant regular hits over 100s....not too mention the 5 second stun proc also dds for 90 dmg.  Needless to say I love this weapon.  Just wanted to add some facts, on with crushing !<BR>
<BR>
you crush a sepulcher skeleton for 97<BR>
you crush a sepulcher skeleton for 78<BR>
a sepulcher skeleton is hit for non melee (90)<BR>
a sepulcher skeleton is stunned<BR>
muahaha and I had Landiaz(59 enc)  can u say "wonderous rapidity?"  OWNAGE to the 18th power ! ! !<BR>
